    "Such methods are commonly employed to extract meaningful information and patterns from complex and highdimensional RS data.",
    "In summation, the effectiveness of AI algorithms in the realms of precision agriculture, crop monitoring, pest and disease identification, input resources optimization, data analytics, and crop yield simulation has been substantiated through empirical evidence.",
